This paper deals with the integration of Description Logics and Logic Programming, which are both subfields of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the satisfiability checking of knowledge bases, which is a topic in Logic (cs.LO) and Databases (cs.DB). The use of guarded logic programs is a technique commonly used in Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Programming Languages (cs.PL). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
